{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2805734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先，招生简章原话是“6.通过强基计划录取的学生入校后原则上不得转到录取专业之外的专业就读。”", "timestamp": 1635330291, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805741, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "咱们暂且不论“原则上”三个字有多大的可操作性，先看专业，强基计划的专业是什么？他是这么给出的", "timestamp": 1635330344, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805742, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1827, "w": 1079}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1635330354, "type": "image", "url": "cm/cmwe3by54ahvy66fzs76fxnaymml2jkt.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2805751, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "也就是说行健的招生专业是理论与应用力学，假设我不知道清华强基计划有什么专业 我去招生专业一栏去看，我看到的是“理论与应用力学”", "timestamp": 1635330428, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？", "timestamp": 1635330436, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805755, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "额…所以呢", "timestamp": 1635330443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805763, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那土木啊，车辆啊是什么呢？你清也发明了一个词，叫“专业衔接方向”", "timestamp": 1635330475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以现在大家明白我要说啥了吧，是不是也可以这么理解……", "timestamp": 1635330509, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805773, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一说一 就算你说出花来 也轮不到你来诠释政策", "timestamp": 1635330532, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "羟基无脑劝退就完事了", "timestamp": 1635330534, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805781, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我的专业是理论与应用力学，我不能转到理论与应用理学之外的专业(而且还是“原则上”不能)，但是专业衔接方向呢？", "timestamp": 1635330570, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805794, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805781, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: ？", "timestamp": 1635330655, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805773, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 确实不归我管，但是管这个事的人这么写政策就是给自己留了后路的", "timestamp": 1635330687, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805814, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805773, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果这么办，结果，好，那就这么办了，结果不好，也留有灰色地带可以退也不叫违背政策，不打脸", "timestamp": 1635330811, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805826, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805773, "tag": null, "text": "但是如今未央这么卷，领导老师们看来就是激起了学生热情，就叫好，受苦的只有学生了", "timestamp": 1635330903, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805781, "tag": null, "text": "如果学生反响不好，那行健土木转到行健车辆，重新掏出来招生简章一看，也没说不允许", "timestamp": 1635331015, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805938, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805781, "tag": null, "text": "所以强基的学弟学妹或许可以问问班主任，辅导员，院长，主任什么的能不能换专业衔接方向，尽管可能性不大，但毕竟是处在政策上的灰色地带，或许可以争取，北大强基不就可以转吗", "timestamp": 1635331833, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805835, "tag": null, "text": "dz八字班，什么强基不强基的跟我没关系，只是涉及学妹，了解了一下。而且本身我就是转过专业的，我知道不能转专业存在极大的不合理性，领导老师们肯定也能认识到这个问题，因此给强基的同学提出一个可能的方向，所以无论你是掉坑了骂强基也好也好，是大类招生想找优越感来显得自己才是最nb的骂强基也罢，请移步，不要逮谁都乱喷，谢谢", "timestamp": 1635332136, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2806510, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "未央是不行的#280961", "timestamp": 1635336449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2807595, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 534412, "reply_to": 2805938, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 八字班，在书院做社工，目前了解是不能", "timestamp": 1635347964, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 534412, "reply": 20, "tag": null, "text": "高三班主任带出来的小学妹现在在行健，跟我聊了好几次不喜欢自己的专业，想学行健的另一个专业，然后我就去看了看官方文件，发现了一些问题，敬请各位洞友看一看有没有道理。", "timestamp": 1635330247, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1635347963, "url": "", "vote": {}}}